Projektname: Kognitive Implikationen der Abwesenheit von Zahlen und Zählsystemen in der Pirahã Sprache



Datenquellen:

A)	Sprachkorpus der Pirahã Sprache:

 „This corpus provides a transcription and word-by-word translation of 1149 sentences of Pirahã that
 were collected during fieldwork by Steve Sheldon and Dan Everett. Our goal is to provide primary
 linguistic data from Pirahã in a human- and machine-readable format that includes annotation of
 the lexicon, morphology, and syntax of the language.“

Link: https://github.com/languageMIT/piraha
